    ^
    k
< h   l >
    j
    V

TO NORMAL MODE
Ctrl-[
Esc

TO INSERT MODE
i - before cursor
a - after cursor
I - before line
A - after line
o - in a new (next) line
O - in a new (prev) line
s - delete char under cursor, then there
S - delete line, then there
c[x] - delete [x], then there
C - delete until end of line, then there

TO VISUAL MODE
v

TO VISUAL LINE
V

TO VISUAL BLOCK
Ctrl-v

TO COMMAND MODE
:
